{"tid":607022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：倘香港遲遲未就23條立法，就可能「北京代你立法」","createTime":"2018-03-27T02:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T03:07:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d256a08e1952aacf063538705ee22f64f3a844","tid":607022,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180327/s00001/f4ba0701a1e06feccbbe57f575332141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180327%2Fs00001%2Ff4ba0701a1e06feccbbe57f575332141.jpg&h=12d8ec91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主思路上周訪京，召集人湯家驊今日出席港台節目，指在訪京期間和京官討論多個議題，包括23條立法和參選權。他提到，為23條立法可能是唯一可掌握的政治籌碼，如拒絕討論，就等於放棄籌碼，甚至「北京代你立法」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊提出《基本法》23條分階段立法，不同京官有不同反應，有較多反面論據，回應仔細，在技術、政治和憲法上的層面質疑湯的方案是否可行。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊希望民主派想清楚，要用什麼策略完成23條立法和政改，他又希望大家明白，若香港遲遲未就23條立法，就可能「北京代你立法」。湯稱，為23條立法可能是唯一尚可掌握的政治籌碼，如拒絕討論，就是放棄唯一的籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n對於參選權的討論，湯不認為需要擁護及效忠共產黨才可有選舉權，但他指京官則認為共產黨在中國執政，有憲法授權，要尊重這個政治事實及一國兩制。他又指，對方表示不接受共產黨即是不接受一國，亦即是不接受一國兩制，若不接受一國兩制的話，則不用參選。"},{"pid":"af538ae5826565b9b083f5d1476c8e6c479e3390","tid":607022,"uid":3241,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"又係十一驊鳩UP"},{"pid":"988fa6f9e0c27a1b629db794c3933c90cb61e594","tid":607022,"uid":104555,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"昨天的我打倒今天的我<br />\n中共肉便器"},{"pid":"42b7ce93a540770c7e6a06f05f6c0b4f78546bbc","tid":607022,"uid":90,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"湯不認為需要擁護及效忠共產黨才可有選舉權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好笑呢句"},{"pid":"e5c91daf5d7f41edb989ef98b51ad0a7576de5b4","tid":607022,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3922afeb7613278f2859486d76fb9339e72c2e50","tid":607022,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"附件3引入國安法咪得囉！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c5dad018677a661872ac6b7a5b61376de4b0cd","tid":607022,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"最佳25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678ad2edb60749f22d73d61a2e7be91fccce2c32","tid":607022,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"同張屌明HEHE完就講呢D野<br />\n睇黎係習近平最高聖旨"},{"pid":"65979e9cc8eda6159d62c7482e842b56c2fa99b5","tid":607022,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"一係你自己除，一係我幫你除"},{"pid":"fc447d126d22f702084c238e219e1fdefe2ee0cd","tid":607022,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/110145_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F110145_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif&h=548489f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27603593b32312c6a39d96619ee5787e694e9042","tid":607022,"uid":71257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:03:40.000Z","msg":"傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家假假地都有立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n北京代立真係立法會都唔洗要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a2d9b7ae8903cda4b9a2b37be0044b3abd046c","tid":607022,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"11哥比人獎勵完? 咁好火力嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6